Hi there <%= @reservation.user.name %>,

Our records show that you were registered for the recent class 
"<%= @reservation.session.topic.name %>".
	
Now that the class has concluded, we'd love to get your feedback!

<% if @reservation.session.topic.survey_type == 1 %>
We've prepared a very quick, 3 question survey that won't take 
more than 2 minutes of your time -- we promise! Please use this
URL to take the survey, and accept our thanks.

<%= url_for :controller => "survey_responses", :action => "new", :only_path => false %>?reservation_id=<%= @reservation.id %>
<% else %>	
The instructor for this course has set up a survey to collect 
feedback on this course. Please use this URL to complete the 
survey. Thank you!

<%=h @reservation.session.topic.survey_url%>
<% end %>

Thanks in advance for your feedback!
